{"tid":1003394,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"長期養病 前路茫茫","createTime":"2019-01-31T15:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T12:00:41.000Z","uid":138954,"like":124,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"20642c6c96ce1564f31eeda137a060c619288382","tid":1003394,"uid":138954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:16:17.000Z","msg":"唉 好頹<br />\n罕見天生問題上年做完大手術<br />\n至今連基本生活都未完全回復到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左去醫院，9成時間坐係屋企與痛為伴，home office freelance工又搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n莫講搭車，出街行下，甚至齋坐都困難重重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完全康復既盡頭仲未見到，雖然家人叫專心休養又冇財政壓力<br />\n但諗起將來就只有一片茫茫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n空白咁耐出番黎做嘢實俾人壓價，辛苦捱病痛，到頭來咪又係回到係香港做奴工慘過做狗既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n身邊既人，院友，姑娘等睇我好開朗好樂觀日日笑keke，其實⋯⋯我好撚頹到唔知講乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999 <br />\n多謝你睇完呢篇冇營養既字<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熄機訓覺聽日繼續作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4584ee65f10a9c798878224cc52b18afb14c9705","tid":1003394,"uid":84415,"like":7,"dislike":48,"score":-41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:19:33.000Z","msg":"起碼你仲有庇護工場接收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ca8212e26d68b9f5191c72380da2a5dec8697d","tid":1003394,"uid":208726,"like":6,"dislike":21,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:19:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9706a35a3eb6de8c7d352b20d9d88947798a6ed7","tid":1003394,"uid":46752,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:20:42.000Z","msg":"加油 現實就係咁樣 只好接受 一切隨緣<br />\n利申：有病"},{"pid":"f7f03568de721bc8469e49fe7ad91c49787accc1","tid":1003394,"uid":22407,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:22:57.000Z","msg":"日後嘅事日後再算<br />\n最重要係安心養傷盡快好返<br />\n我之前都做咗手術 養傷一年咪又搵到工"},{"pid":"5041152537fab4e13c9db64d9a73c97bfbcfa1a4","tid":1003394,"uid":18074,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"呢個世界唔係剩係得份工...世界好大，盡力做到自己想做的野就夠<br />\n<br />\n巴打加油！保持樂觀的心，所有病都會快好！"},{"pid":"2cffc10928ee2e5182d1239204fcf99e0b33ce7d","tid":1003394,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:26:58.000Z","msg":"下世再努力啦，而家都做唔到d 乜"},{"pid":"47ec9eeba647f9a9964224c05ddfa41dea184862","tid":1003394,"uid":196964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:29:31.000Z","msg":"加油 巴打"},{"pid":"0532aa74db0f531c875cde35a34fd00881849f78","tid":1003394,"uid":78666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"頂住啦<br />\n<br />\n難關都過到<br />\n<br />\n日後就會比任何人更堅強"},{"pid":"30a6eafe464a14b9640cc65175193e81324bb522","tid":1003394,"uid":27055,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:33:34.000Z","msg":"巴打專心養好左個病先 無病無痛 再諗下有咩啱自己做 世界不嬲都係咁現實 但同時又無你諗得咁灰 見步行步 就已經會行得好遠 巴打加油! 共勉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d81ce4ad74ee16892d1a02543a4a7c893fa950","tid":1003394,"uid":53872,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"你已經比好多人幸運了"},{"pid":"0d83826d9664320ae2bdf2e860dc70aa00f66f76","tid":1003394,"uid":65384,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"加油 <br />\n我而家都有長期病 要成日覆診食藥<br />\n返工成日都要請假<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲啲都可能要做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打專心養好病 其他野遲啲先諗啦"},{"pid":"06e96ee971a00d1c94cdeb3e461f0edcbca69c05","tid":1003394,"uid":52132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:36:31.000Z","msg":"幾歲呀爸打？"},{"pid":"215ef0b9b892930d6cc13ec1f036790944285fe4","tid":1003394,"uid":16